item.title: Residential Prices
item.dc:creator: root
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]

Lock Re-Keys

Moved to a new home? Re-key your door and mailbox locks. Be certain no stranger has a spare key. We’re here to keep you secure. Call Now
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]

New Installations

A new door needs a new lock. We install plain and decorative locks, mailboxes and padlocks. Don’t hesitate, call for a free quote. Call Now
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1500554160592{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;padding-top: 100px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;background-color: #f2f2f2 !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]

Lock Picking

Did you find yourself locked outside? Picking a lock doesn’t take long. We’ll get you back in and we won’t tell. Call Now
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]

Security Lock Systems

Do you need something extra? Ask us about high security locks, master keys, keyless or digital entry systems and other options. Call Now
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]

Lock Repairs

Have a lock with a “temper”? Do not wait with a faulty lock it is more than an inconvenience, in an emergency it’s a hazard. Call Now
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]

Anything with a lock

Not everything with a lock is a door. We also service locks in sliding glass doors, french doors, windows and any other type of lock. Call Now
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]
